title: Alumni Resources: Libraries - Northwestern University
content: A Northwestern NetID is required to access secure online resources. Alumni can request temporary NetIDs to access resources on a library computer by visiting a library service desk. Learn more Alumni who live in the Chicago area are eligible for borrowing privileges at Northwestern Libraries. For borrowing privileges, please fill out our online form to begin the application process.
